title: EYL #209 The Business of Daycare Centers, Real Estate, & Entrepreneurship
itunes:title: EYL #209 The Business of Daycare Centers, Real Estate, & Entrepreneurship
description:
In this episode Casanova Brooks talked about his journey to become a top real estate agent, investing in real estate, the business of daycare centers, entrepreneurship, and more.

He also discussed his amazing life story winch includes beating cancer, surviving homelessness, and beating the odds after the death of his mother and grandmother. #business #daycarecenters #realestate
